query:
UPDATE project_boards
                 SET name = $2,
                     slug = $3,
                     board_type = $4,
                     description = $5,
                     metadata = $6,
                     updated_at = datetime('now', 'subsec')
               WHERE id = $1
               RETURNING
                id as "id!: Uuid",
                project_id as "project_id!: Uuid",
                name,
                slug,
                board_type as "board_type!: ProjectBoardType",
                description,
                metadata,
                created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>",
                updated_at as "updated_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
